‚Ä¢	InnoDB supports Row-level Locking
‚Ä¢	InnoDB designed for maximum performance when processing high volume of data
‚Ä¢	InnoDB support foreign keys hence we call MySQL with InnoDB is RDBMS
‚Ä¢	InnoDB stores its tables and indexes in a tablespace
‚Ä¢	InnoDB supports transaction. You can commit and rollback with InnoDB

